{"tid":697662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本土港獨義士係時候放棄用連登宣傳","createTime":"2018-06-11T05:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T16:47:55.000Z","uid":4493,"like":77,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a844854f996683ce448296444878c18f37719d","tid":697662,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"今日判刑，可見時事台人流已經好少，一早因為連囝縱容五毛走鬼晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n剩低嘅一係五毛，一係唔理政治，一係已經係自己人圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋嘅目標觀眾根本唔喺度<br />\n<br />\n長江後浪推前浪，想做大個餅一定要向新一代落手，抗衡支那洗腦，讓香港人有凖備等機會成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同時祝入嚟嘅五毛：<br />\n<br />\n留言一次染愛滋<br />\n留言兩次仆街暴斃<br />\n留言三次全家死清光<br />\n留言四次永遠做支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6d9d3a725a7459ee952c7ded16a67b166e0d9e","tid":697662,"uid":157362,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04c1cf5c71c227140e7bde80bc6c4f59c5f9fe4b","tid":697662,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70c810fed50ddcd1eaa7d7416aedaa92cde4541b","tid":697662,"uid":4493,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd6d9d3a725a7459ee952c7ded16a67b166e0d9e","tid":697662,"uid":157362,"like":11,"dislike":6,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:00:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:01:45.000Z","msg":"愛滋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b7b37f86630b0f36e9a3aeb5c90c6675ab6a44","tid":697662,"uid":157362,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:02:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89cdca3e469c987f094d01417d0b7b42d0eaf18c","tid":697662,"uid":157362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018